<HEADLINE>
<P>
ON THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
"(Federal Reserve Chairman Alan) Greenspan likes to dig into the numbers, and 
what he's seeing raises some warning signs." 
</P>
<P>
 -- Bush Administration official, explaining the Fed's long-awaited move last 
week to ease interest rates. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA111289-0034 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 133524 </DOCID>
