pleasure in the article by Nick Clooney ("Memories Are Made of This"); we 
especially enjoyed Jerry Hulse's story ("Sheer Grace: A Visit to Madewood, 
Queen of the Bayou") and found "Lunar Holiday" by Willis Player to be 
particularly fascinating. 
