<P>
SOUTHWEST BEATS HARBOR, 30-12 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By KEN BANKS 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The L.A. Southwest College football team held Harbor College scoreless in the 
second half of their Western State Conference contest Saturday and capitalized 
on several Seahawk miscues for a 30-12 victory. 
</P>
<P>
