BUILDER OF THE YEAR 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Dale Stuard, founder of American National Housing and Stuard Industries, has 
been named 1989 Builder of the Year by the Building Association of Southern 
California. 
</P>
<P>
Stuard has been a home builder for more than 36 years and is immediate past 
president of the National Assn. of Home Builders. 
</P>
<P>
Stuard Industries develops projects located primarily in Orange, Riverside and 
SanBernardino counties. 
