CLARIFICATION 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Times' critique of architect I. M. Pei's headquarters building for Creative 
Artists Agency ("Pei Masterpiece: Too Elegant Here?" Oct. 22) inadvertently 
omitted the name of the project's executive architect, the Los Angeles firm of 
Langdon Wilson. 
</P>
